Summary: large square or H shaped plane like craft escorted by normal plane. flying south to north.
divs: Sighting DetailsNot like any aircraft ive ever seen. Seemed to have two sets of wings like a capital H. Significantly larger than a 747. Being escorted by a standard commercial type aircraft to the west. The two crafts cruised at approx 25,000 feet right along the coast. They continued north until out of sight.
